3088:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @brief  Helper macro to set the value of ADC analog watchdog threshold high
3089:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         or low in function of ADC resolution, when ADC resolution is
