3429:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                TS_CAL2   = equivalent TS_ADC_DATA at temperature
3430:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *                            TEMP_DEGC_CAL2 (calibrated in factory)
3431:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         Caution: Calculation relevancy under reserve that calibration
