4082:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   * @note   On STM32G4, some fast channels are available: fast analog inputs
4083:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32g4xx_ll_adc.h ****   *         coming from GPIO pads (ADC_IN1..5).
