 223:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc.c ****      The compilation flag USE_HAL_ADC_REGISTER_CALLBACKS, when set to 1,
 224:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc.c ****      allows the user to configure dynamically the driver callbacks.
