 244:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc.c **** 
 245:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc.c ****      Use function @ref HAL_ADC_UnRegisterCallback to reset a callback to the default
 246:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc.c ****      weak function.
 247:Drivers/STM32G4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g4xx_hal_adc.c ****     [..]
